name: Thank You Goddexx 4 Making Me Nonbinary
description:
Originally posted on Instagram on March 31, 2020, with the following caption: 

Happy #transdayofvisibility! I am so honored and grateful to be a part of the sacred #transcommunity and to be able to define what my #nonbinary #genders look like for me! As a loving reminder, I use they / them / theirs pronouns professionally and am fluid, contextual, and subjective with my he/she/they/ze/xe/ellx/etc. pronouns with friends and loved ones! 

Sending out an immense amount of care & protection to our divine queer, transgender, and gender-expansive communities!!! 
.
Limited edition of 100 by Edgar Fabián Frías / @edgarfabianfrias | 720 x 720 | .mp4 | 2020. Minted on December 27, 2021.
